data.description: THIS IS YOUR FOREVER HOME!  See one and be done! This move in ready ranch home is the one you've been waiting for.  Upon entry, you will notice the beautiful, original hardwood floors.  The living room has plenty of space for a large sectional so everyone has a seat for cozy movie days or the upcoming big game. Down the hall you will find an updated bathroom and three spacious bedrooms with nice sized closets.  There is a formal dining area that could be used as a den or a play room just off of the kitchen.  The large kitchen has a ton of cabinet and counter top space, great for storage and hosting get togethers.  The kitchen and laundry room both have brand new flooring and there is fresh paint throughout the whole house. Out back, you will notice a HUGE dethatched garage, a very large privacy fenced in yard that includes a pergola and a fire pit.  For those who love an intimate backyard oasis, this has a lot of potential!  Located conveniently to interstate access, shopping and more!
